This paper is about stabilizing the training dynamics of GANs, which is a problem in the field of machine learning. The paper uses control theory to model and stabilize the dynamics, which is a subfield of systems engineering. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
